						<m>(P\lor Q)\land R</m> and <m>P\lor (Q\land R)</m>
					</p>
				</li>
		
				<li>
					<p>
						<m>P\Rightarrow Q</m> and <m>(\sim P)\lor Q</m>
					</p>
				</li>
		
