			</p>
		
			<p>
				<em>Remark.</em> You may retain non-logic symbols like <m>\geq</m> and <m>=</m>, but try to avoid <m>\in</m>. For this exercise, <q>there exists a real number <m>x</m></q> is preferable to “there exists <m>x\in{\bf R}</m>.
